ign:center;">\r\n	<img width="642" height="175" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328a369f177.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">短信充值界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="643" height="95" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328a423ae5a.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">短信余额页面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">新建账号后，在“短信充值记录”页面的“充值金额”中输入要充值的金额，点击“微信扫码支付”，进入扫码支付页面，扫码二维码支付金额。然后在“短信账号”页面可查看余额。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;">2.3<span>微信设置</span></span><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;">2.3.1<span>微信支付设置</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">微信支付设置用于设置在线支付账号信息的填写。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="643" height="312" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328a4db097e.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">微信支付设置界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">按要求正确填写信息，即可将在将用户在线支付金额支付到指定账号中。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;">2.3.2<span>微信链接设置</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">微信链接设置用于生成微信访问首页网址。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="642" height="71" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328aba07a50.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">微信链接设置界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">复制“微信链接”中的网址到微信公众账号自定义菜单下即可访问店铺首页。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="384" height="608" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328adf984fe.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">已设置好的微信页面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>            ', '', 0, 0),
