an> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">角色管理用于新建角色权限使用。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n		<img width="388" height="264" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328c04c7a32.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">添加角色界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">在“添加角色”界面新建角色，然后在“角色管理”界面点击“权限设置”选择该角色分配权限。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n		<img width="266" height="323" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328c0d34621.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">权限设置界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<h2>\r\n		<span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;">3.3<span>部门与员工</span></span><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n	</h2>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n		<img width="643" height="152" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57328c1ce346c.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">部门管理界面</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28.0000pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">部门管理用于填写公司部门，所填写部门可以在账号管理中显示，并可根据部门发送信息。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', '', 0, 0);
