(18, '结算统计', '', '                <h2>\r\n	<span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;">8.1<span>对账详单</span></span><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="642" height="247" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57329c92470ea.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">对账详单</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:28pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">对账详单默认显示当日全部订单明细，也可以显示指点时间内订单的全部详情，检索区分为日期检索，商家检索，订单<span>ID</span><span>检索，订单类型检索（订单类型包含货到付款、在线支付、快速下单），查询到相应的数据点击“导出</span><span>excel</span><span>”可以导出为</span><span>excel</span><span>文件。</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<img width="197" height="38" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57329c9cb3285.png" align="left" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;">订单详情区内，点击订单<span>ID</span><span>可显示订单详情；合计显示选择的时间段内所有订单的全部合计；订单总计</span><span>=</span><span>菜品原价</span><span>+</span><span>配送费</span><span>+</span><span>打包费—活动减免。</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;">8.2<span>商家结算报表</span></span><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:16pt;"></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="643" height="259" src="/Uploads/2016-05-11/57329ca5cbb21.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;">商家结算报表（图<span>26</span><span>）</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> \r\n