(26, '微信支付设置帮助（1）', '', '<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;">第一步：打开平台“设置”-》“微信支付设置”，出现如下界面：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="554" height="320" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/5734425e09773.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">备注（请认真阅读）：以上信息需要分别从您的“微信公众平台”和“商户平台”里获得，微信公众平台（服务号）需要您自已申请，申请地址：</span><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com"><span class="15" style="font-family:宋体;color:#0000FF;font-size:12pt;">https://mp.weixin.qq.com</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">，有了微信公众账号后，需要在公众账号里开开通“微信支付”，开通微信支付后，微信会给您发送电子邮件确认开通成功，如下图：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img width="449" height="151" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/5734426a32732.png" /><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;">第二步：获得以上信息并保存好，填入到平台中进行保存即可</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">下面介绍已经有了“微信公众平台”和“商户平台”的用户获得以上信息具体的方法，见下表，建议您把以上信息先用文本文件收集好，然后再一次性录入到平台中。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<table class="MsoTableGrid" style="border-collapse:collapse;width:426.1000pt;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;">信息</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;">获得方法</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">商名名称</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">自己填写即可，可以起成您公司的名子如：肯德基</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">商户号</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录微信公众平台，地址：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com">https://mp.weixin.qq.com</a></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">点击公众平台里的“微信支付”菜单，如下图：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="393" height="240" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/57344276572cf.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">APPID和APPSECRET</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录微信公众平台，地址：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com">https://mp.weixin.qq.com</a></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">点击“微信公众平台”里的“开发”-》“基本配置”菜单，如下图：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="172" height="159" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/5734428008644.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">在右侧界面显示出基本配置信息，其中</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#FF0000;font-size:12.0000pt;">Appid(应用ID)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">后面的一串英文就是appid，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#FF0000;font-size:12.0000pt;">AppSecret（应用密钥）</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">就是AppSecret</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="469" height="268" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/57344288da164.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">KEY</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录“商户平台”，地址：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><a href="https://pay.weixin.qq.com">https://pay.weixin.qq.com</a></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">用户名和密码在您收到</span><span style="font-family:Verdana;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;">微信支付商户资料审核</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;">通过的电子邮件里</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录后，点击“API安全”会看到如下界面，点击“设置密钥”设置您自已的密钥，这个密钥就是平台需要的，如下您看不到这个界面，请先安装证书</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="202" height="158" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/573442a1899c2.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="232" height="231" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/573442adeb757.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">商户证书(cert)和</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">商户证书(key)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录“商户平台”，地址：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><a href="https://pay.weixin.qq.com">https://pay.weixin.qq.com</a></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">用户名和密码在您收到</span><span style="font-family:Verdana;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;">微信支付商户资料审核</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;">通过的电子邮件里</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">登录后，点击“API安全”会看到如下界面，点击“下载证书”</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">证书下载后是一个压缩包，解压后，里面的</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">apiclient_cert.pem</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">是商户证书(cert),</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">apiclient_key.pem</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;">是商户证书(key)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.5pt;background:#E4ECF5;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"><img width="400" height="293" src="/Uploads/2016-05-12/573442b615c5e.png" /></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width="86" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width="482" valign="top" style="border:0.5000pt solid #000000;">\r\n				<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;"></span> \r\n</p>', '', 0, 0),
(27, '微信支付设置帮助（2）', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n	<strong>支付授权设置</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:0pt;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	登陆企业账号，依次进入“系统设置<span>-</span><span>微信设置</span><span>-</span><span>微信支付设置”，点击“微信支付目录设置”的“复制”按钮，复制地址。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="/Uploads/2016-05-13/57356f03bb2fd.png" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	登陆微信公众账号依次进入“微信支付<span>-</span><span>开发设置”，点击“支付授权目录”后的“修改”按钮，粘贴刚才复制的信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<span><img src="/Uploads/2016-05-13/57356f0d80101.png" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', 0, 0),
(28, '客户注册与安全认证', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21.1000pt;text-align:center;">\r\n	<strong>客户注册与安全认证</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:0.0000pt;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	登陆企业账号，依次进入“系统设置<span>-</span><span>微信设置</span><span>-</span><span>微信链接设置”，点击“网页授权获取用户基本信息”的“复制”按钮，复制地址。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<span><img src="/Uploads/2016-05-13/57356f6e89a7b.png" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:0.0000pt;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	登陆微信公众账号依次进入“公众号设置<span>-</span><span>功能设置”，点击“业务域名”后的“修改”按钮，粘贴刚才复制的信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<span><img src="/Uploads/2016-05-13/57356f7d9374d.png" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	然后进入“接口权限”，点击“网页服务<span>-</span><span>网页账号”后的“修改”按钮，再次粘贴刚才复制的信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;">\r\n	<span><img src="/Uploads/2016-05-13/57356f89e38e2.png" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>', '', 0, 0);
